description:
The Solid-Optics Multi-Fiber-Tool is designed for network professionals. This software requires a Multi-Fiber-Tool which can be acquired through Solid Optics. 

This app has several functionalities:

1) recode or rebrand SFP(+), XFP and QSFP modules from Solid Optics to work with routers/switches from other manufacturers;

2) set the channel of tunable XFP or SFP+ DWDM optics;

3) Read the optical power from a LC-terminated fiber with the multi-fiber-tool 3 or a seperate power read optic.
